    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is 1. to describe levofloxacin pharmacokinetics in ICU patients
      suffering from pneumonia with taking into account physio-pathological parameters. 2. to
      verify clinical and bacteriological efficiency and to know if the peak/Minimum Inhibitory
      Concentration (MIC) ratio &gt; 5 and Area Under Curve (AUC) /Minimum Inhibitory
      Concentration(MIC) ratio &gt; 125. No therapeutic drug monitoring will be performed in this
      study.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
