  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  severe community-acquired pneumonia due to a strain sensible to levofloxacin

          -  Age &gt; 18 years

          -  Informed consent

          -  SAPS II (simplified acute physiological score) &gt; 20 Awaited duration of survival
             higher than 7 days

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Historic of allergy to levofloxacin

          -  Resistant strain to levofloxacin

          -  Pregnancy

          -  Contra-indications of levofloxacin use, renal failure
      </textblock>
